      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or for parts. The engine currently struggles to start and requires significant mechanical attention, while the exterior shows noticeable rust patches, several large dents, and fading clear coat. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears, and several electronic components, including the radio and power windows, are non-functional. It will likely need to be towed from the lot, but it offers a complete set of original components for someone willing to put in the work.",
